title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 24 2022

description:
What will Biden do? Why Ukraine matters. New Zealand goes on full lockdown over Omicron. Does Biden want a war in Ukraine to boost his poll numbers? Host of The View says she may wear a mask forever. California school board meeting shut down for mask-wearing violation. U.S. troops on alert for deployment to NATO countries.
